Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.99,Sign #3,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\c&H44407B&\fs36\pos(238.6,33)}Essa LN é ótima!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.99,Sign #4,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\blur1\pos(640,276)\c&HE7CB9A&}Blog de Notícias de LN
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem, um descanso não fará mal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Espere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu estraguei outro dia inteiro!
